### ============================================================
### POST — Tạo activity log
### ============================================================

### 1. Tạo log CREATE TASK
POST {{baseUrl}}/activities
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "CREATE",
  "entityType": "TASK",
  "entityId": 1,
  "projectId": null,
  "ipAddress": "192.168.1.1",
  "metadata": "{\"taskName\": \"Thiết kế UI màn hình đăng nhập\", \"priority\": \"HIGH\"}"
}

###

### 2. Tạo log UPDATE TASK
POST {{baseUrl}}/activities
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "UPDATE",
  "entityType": "TASK",
  "entityId": 1,
  "projectId": null,
  "ipAddress": "192.168.1.1",
  "metadata": "{\"field\": \"status\", \"oldValue\": \"TODO\", \"newValue\": \"IN_PROGRESS\"}"
}

###

### 3. Tạo log LOGIN USER
POST {{baseUrl}}/activities
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "LOGIN",
  "entityType": "USER",
  "entityId": 7,
  "projectId": null,
  "ipAddress": "10.0.0.1",
  "metadata": "{\"device\": \"Chrome/Windows\", \"os\": \"Windows 11\"}"
}

###

### 4. Tạo log CREATE COMMENT
POST {{baseUrl}}/activities
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "CREATE",
  "entityType": "COMMENT",
  "entityId": 1,
  "projectId": null,
  "ipAddress": "192.168.1.1",
  "metadata": "{\"commentPreview\": \"Cần review lại phần màu sắc\", \"taskId\": 1}"
}

###

### 5. Tạo log UPLOAD ATTACHMENT
POST {{baseUrl}}/activities
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "UPLOAD",
  "entityType": "ATTACHMENT",
  "entityId": 1,
  "projectId": null,
  "ipAddress": "192.168.1.1",
  "metadata": "{\"fileName\": \"API_docs.pdf\", \"fileSize\": \"2.5MB\", \"entityType\": \"TASK\"}"
}

###

### ============================================================
### POST EDGE CASES
### ============================================================

### 6. Thiếu action → expect 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/activities
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "entityType": "TASK",
  "entityId": 1,
  "metadata": "{\"taskName\": \"Test\"}"
}

###

### 7. Thiếu entityType → expect 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/activities
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "CREATE",
  "entityId": 1,
  "metadata": "{\"taskName\": \"Test\"}"
}

###

### 8. Thiếu entityId → expect 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/activities
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "CREATE",
  "entityType": "TASK",
  "metadata": "{\"taskName\": \"Test\"}"
}

###

### 9. Không có token → expect 401
POST {{baseUrl}}/activities
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "CREATE",
  "entityType": "TASK",
  "entityId": 1,
  "metadata": "{\"taskName\": \"Test\"}"
}

###

### ============================================================
### DELETE — Xóa log cũ (Admin only)
### ============================================================

### 10. Admin xóa log trước ngày 2026-04-02
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/activities
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "before": "2026-04-02T00:00:00"
}

###

### 11. Admin xóa log trước ngày 2026-04-03
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/activities
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "before": "2026-04-03T00:00:00"
}

###

### 12. Admin xóa toàn bộ log trước hôm nay
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/activities
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "before": "2026-05-04T00:00:00"
}

