### ============================================================
### DELETE EDGE CASES
### ============================================================

### 13. User thường gọi delete → expect 403
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/activities
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "before": "2026-04-02T00:00:00"
}

###

### 14. Thiếu before → expect 400
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/activities
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

###

### 15. Không có token → expect 401
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/activities
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "before": "2026-04-02T00:00:00"
}